OL,6,FThey are described as white, wearing
OL,7,Fdark clothing and a dark-coloured
OL,8,Frucksack. Their face was mostly
OL,9,Fcovered by a beanie hat or similar
OL,10,Fthat had been pulled down.
OL,12,FGuernsey Police says: "This was a
OL,13,Fparticularly violent offence and
OL,14,FCrimestoppers is offering a reward of
OL,15,F#750 for information leading to the
OL,16,Farrest, charge and conviction of the
OL,17,Foffender."
